<ng-container *ngIf="labelKey">
  <ng-container *ngIf="!groupBy">
    <ng-select [items]="optionList" [bindLabel]="labelKey" [bindValue]="inputKey" [(ngModel)]="value"
      [placeholder]="placeholder" [tabIndex]="tabIndex" (change)="changeEvent.emit($event)">
    </ng-select>
  </ng-container>

  <ng-container *ngIf="groupBy">

    <ng-select [items]="optionList" [bindLabel]="labelKey" [bindValue]="inputKey" [groupBy]="groupBy"
      [(ngModel)]="value" [placeholder]="placeholder" [tabIndex]="tabIndex" (change)="changeEvent.emit($event)">
      <ng-template ng-optgroup-tmp let-item="item">
        {{item[groupBy] || 'Unnamed group'}}
      </ng-template>
    </ng-select>
  </ng-container>
</ng-container>

<ng-container *ngIf="!labelKey">
  <ng-select [items]="optionList" [(ngModel)]="value" [placeholder]="placeholder" [tabIndex]="tabIndex"
    (change)="changeEvent.emit($event)">
  </ng-select>
</ng-container>

<ng-container *ngIf="parentForm">
  <fn-input-error [position]="'bottom'" [submitted]="parentForm.submitted" [control]="parentForm.form.controls[name]"
    [tabIndex]="tabIndex">
  </fn-input-error>
</ng-container>

<ng-container>
  <ng-container *ngIf="!groupBy">
    <ng-select [items]="optionList" [multiple]="true" [maxSelectedItems]="" [bindLabel]="labelKey" [(ngModel)]="value"
      [placeholder]="placeholder" [tabIndex]="tabIndex" (change)="changeEvent.emit($event)">
    </ng-select>
  </ng-container>

  <ng-container *ngIf="groupBy">

    <ng-select [items]="optionList" [multiple]="true" [groupBy]="groupBy" [maxSelectedItems]="" [bindLabel]="labelKey"
      [(ngModel)]="value" [placeholder]="placeholder" [tabIndex]="tabIndex" (change)="changeEvent.emit($event)">

      <ng-template ng-optgroup-tmp let-item="item">
        {{item[groupBy] || 'Unnamed group'}}
      </ng-template>
    </ng-select>
  </ng-container>
</ng-container>


<ng-container *ngIf="parentForm">
  <fn-input-error [position]="'bottom'" [submitted]="parentForm.submitted" [control]="parentForm.form.controls[name]"
    [tabIndex]="tabIndex">
  </fn-input-error>
</ng-container>
